title: Erdogan meets Pope Francis at the Vatican
text:
Erdogan meets Pope Francis at the Vatican 12:24pm GMT - 00:47 
Turkish President Tayyip Erdogan met with Pope Francis at the Vatican in talks focused on Jerusalem and peace efforts in the Middle East. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
